    "Clustering was done with the Leiden algorithm 97 implemented in scanpy.",
    "Annotating the Brain data set.",
    "Cells with counts less than 5 and more than 300 were removed (2980 out of 26348).",
    "The top 100 highly variable genes (scanpy.experimental.pp.highly_variable_gene(., flavor='pearson_residuals')) were used for normalization, embedding and annotations.",
    "PCA was performed on pearson residuals, and the neighborhood graph was created with this command scanpy.pp.neighbors(., n_neighbors = 20, n_pcs = 15, metric='cosine')."
